    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Drain your<strong> tofu</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Chop the <strong>tofu</strong> lengthways into 2 slices per person and score a criss-cross pattern by drawing a sharp knife through each slice (be careful not to cut all the way through!)</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-tray-spanish-style-tofu-and-pepper-bake/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop into large pieces</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-tray-spanish-style-tofu-and-pepper-bake/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>tomato paste </strong>and <strong>soy sauce </strong>with your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>dried oregano </strong>and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) in a bowl</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> your <strong>red wine vinegar </strong>(save the rest for later!), 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>and stir it all together \u2013 this is your<strong> marinade</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-tray-spanish-style-tofu-and-pepper-bake/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>sliced tofu</strong> to the <strong>marinade</strong> and give it a good mix, then transfer to a baking tray (or two!), keeping the remaining marinade in the bowl (you'll use this later!)</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-tray-spanish-style-tofu-and-pepper-bake/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>black olives</strong> to the <strong>remaining marinade</strong> and give everything a good mix up \u2013 these are your <strong>marinated vegetables</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>marinated vegetables</strong> to the baking tray[s] with the tofu and reserve the bowl</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until everything is cooked through and starting to char</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-tray-spanish-style-tofu-and-pepper-bake/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wipe the reserved bowl clean with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>remaining garlic </strong>(not a fan of raw garlic? Just add a little!),<strong> remaining red wine vinegar</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> cold water </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in the reserved bowl \u2013 this is your <strong>aioli</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-tray-spanish-style-tofu-and-pepper-bake/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once your marinated vegetables are cooked through and charred, remove the tray[s] from the oven</p><p>Add the <strong>spinach</strong> to the baking tray[s] and return to the oven for a final 1-2 min, or until wilted \u2013 this is your <strong>one tray Spanish-style tofu & pepper bake</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-tray-spanish-style-tofu-and-pepper-bake/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>one tray</strong> <strong>Spanish-style tofu & pepper bake</strong> and drizzle with the <strong>aioli</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
